DeathSteel::

He looked at Tyrael. "I come from an old planet. One that is ruled by 
the Decepticons. I was on a mission to get to a moon so we could fix 
the solar power collectors when a black hole hole opened up and 
pulled my ship into it.  When I came out the other side, my ship was 
about to fall apart. I laned here."
